<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4563784>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 22. Anoplodactylus viridintestinalis, UANL-FCB-PYCNO-0082, immature male: A, cephalon, lateral view; B, proboscis, showing mouth, frontal view; C, cephalon, frontal view; D, chelae, enlarged; E, cephalon, ventral view; F, complete specimen, lateral view; G, third leg; H, tarsus, propodus, and claw, enlarged; I, coxa 2, showing gonopore; J, abdomen, lateral view; Scale bars: F = 2 mm; G = 1 mm; A, C, E, J = 0.5 mm; H = 0.3 mm; D, I = 0.2 mm; B = 0.1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4563784/files/figure.png" .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4563740>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 1. Area of study showing the nine marine docks located along the peninsular coast of the Gulf of California, Mexico. 1 = Cabo San Lucas; 2 = Puerto Los Cabos; 3 = FONATUR-Fidepaz; 4 = La Paz; 5 = Fiscal Pier, 6 = Palmira, 7 = Cantamar; 8 = Puerto Escondido (located about 50 km south of Loreto), and 9 = FONATUR-Santa Rosalía, Baja California Sur, Mexico. A magnification of the map shown marine docks 3–7 located at Bahía de La Paz." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4563740/files/figure.png" .

